<h1>--Some initial draft longer-form copy, we will be doing a few of these as text options and in different styles:</h1>

<p>Locally produced, organic and homemade items from the producers direct to you {Anytown} Farmers Market is held weekly in the town market square, offering you a varied selection of well-priced and locally sourced food and related items. We aim to provide a welcoming atmosphere where everyone is catered for and where you can enjoy a gentle stroll to take in the sights and smells or you can search out that unusual ingredient for your latest culinary creation. Our website allows you to search our list of producers, find out when the next market takes place and even take away some delicious recipes to use some of the wonderful products that are sold at our market.</p>
